<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-return-for-sth">in return (for sth)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>作为 (…的) 交换; 作为 (…的) 回报：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If we smile at life, life will smile on us in return.  
如果我们微笑地面对生活，生活也会以微笑回报我们。</p><footer>2009 福建</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wish I could do something in return for the kindness I have received from him. 
我希望自己能做点什么以回报他对我的好意。</p></div></div>